51:48.160 --> 51:50.196
- Nedda?
- What?

51:51.240 --> 51:55.119
- Would you like to go Greek with me?
- Yeah! Hang on, my bra snapped.

51:56.040 --> 51:58.031
For old times' sake.

52:04.040 --> 52:07.157
Me and three of the guys
tightened that up.

52:09.960 --> 52:12.997
