55:46.640 --> 55:49.154
Sorry I'm late. Get off my back.

55:51.640 --> 55:54.438
I think we should go to your place.

55:57.320 --> 55:59.311
I think so.

56:07.000 --> 56:09.958
I really like you
but does it have to be tonight?

56:11.000 --> 56:12.991
Who says?

57:24.040 --> 57:26.031
- I'm OK.
- Are you OK?

57:43.720 --> 57:46.075
You got something?

57:46.120 --> 57:48.429
- You mean rubbers?
- Yeah.

57:50.200 --> 57:53.988
- Talk about a mood changer.
- Well, do you?

57:56.720 --> 58:01.191
The truth is I didn't think this
