58:42.640 --> 58:44.995
- You want a sandwich?
- A sandwich?

58:47.280 --> 58:51.717
I hate wearing goddamn rubbers,
pardon my French. I know you have to.

58:51.760 --> 58:54.638
I never thought I'd contemplate
sleeping with a man

58:54.680 --> 58:57.638
who said "Pardon my French"
all the time.

58:57.680 --> 59:00.274
