Where do you pick up
an expression like that?

59:04.800 --> 59:07.917
- This is good. You made this?
- No, my mum.

59:08.960 --> 59:11.190
- Shit.
- Let me see that.

59:11.240 --> 59:13.549
- It's all right.
- I'll get you something.

59:13.600 --> 59:17.878
Just keep pressure on it. Don't
