59:17.920 --> 59:20.275
I don't think this is gonna work out.

59:20.320 --> 59:22.356
I can't hear what you're saying.

59:22.400 --> 59:26.154
I'm a BLT-down sort of person,

59:26.200 --> 59:29.829
I think you're looking for
someone a little more

59:29.880 --> 59:32.075
pheasant-under-glass.

59:34.760 --> 59:38.799
- What are you doing in there?
- I'm just looking for Band-Aids.

59:39.920 --> 59:42.639
- What are you doing?
- Come on in. Sit down.

59:42.680 --> 59:44.671
I know first aid.

59:46.480 --> 59:48.948
Give me your finger.

59:49.000 --> 59:50.991
Give me your thumb.

