- I'm 32.
- Really? You don't look it.

01:00:19.040 --> 01:00:21.838
- I'm 44.
- Honest?

01:00:23.800 --> 01:00:26.314
I'm gonna be 46 this year.

01:00:30.040 --> 01:00:32.031
