about things like my age.

01:00:37.800 --> 01:00:40.792
I'll be 35 on the 11th of November.

01:00:40.840 --> 01:00:42.876
You're a Scorpio?

01:01:08.360 --> 01:01:11.670
Look in the medicine cabinet.
I have some.

01:01:13.800 --> 01:01:16.837
