to get the wrong impression.

01:01:31.680 --> 01:01:34.353
- They're behind the blue...
- I got 'em.

01:01:48.640 --> 01:01:50.870
Is it on?

01:01:54.440 --> 01:01:57.955
Not yet. You can't just
put it on until it's...

01:01:58.800 --> 01:02:00.791
No, I know.

01:02:15.480 --> 01:02:19.314
You know, I wouldn't have gotten
the wrong impression.

01:03:33.240 --> 01:03:36.038
Let me hear you. I wanna hear you.

01:03:40.520 --> 01:03:43.876
Come on, baby, let it go. Let it go.

01:03:43.920 --> 01:03:46.309
Come on. Let it go. Come on.

01:04:53.640 --> 01:04:56.438
