01:05:23.040 --> 01:05:25.508
Shit like this chokes me up.

01:05:26.800 --> 01:05:29.234
Frankie, come here, touch the baby.

01:05:29.280 --> 01:05:32.158
No, that's OK.
My hands are dirty. Next time.

01:05:32.200 --> 01:05:35.476
This is your last chance.
I am never getting pregnant again.

01:05:35.520 --> 01:05:39.195
You said last time!
Flora, the blue, remember?

01:05:39.240 --> 01:05:42.994
Blue is for the morning.
The red one is for the evening.

01:05:43.040 --> 01:05:46.749
- Thank you.
- You're welcome. Two eggs over-easy.

01:05:46.800 --> 01:05:48.711
Hello to you, too.

01:05:50.600 --> 01:05:53.034
I see you made it home all right.

01:05:54.080 --> 01:05:58.517
Yes, I made it here this morning,
had time enough to put this together.

01:05:58.560 --> 01:06:01.199
- Nice.
- I slept like a babe.

01:06:02.280 --> 01:06:04.840
So, I saw you over there,
you like kids?

01:06:06.840 --> 01:06:09.832
- They're OK.
- You look someone who likes kids.

01:06:09.880 --> 01:06:11.836
Yeah? So did my father.

01:06:11.880 --> 01:06:15.111
What does somebody
who likes kids look like?

01:06:16.720 --> 01:06:20.793
I need an order
of liver and onions... Captain Ahab.

01:06:25.600 --> 01:06:28.398
