out and you keep saying no. Why?

01:07:47.840 --> 01:07:50.070
I'm retired from dating.

01:07:50.120 --> 01:07:54.398
What does that mean? Something
happened when you were a kid?

01:07:54.440 --> 01:07:57.830
Why is it that any time
a women doesn't want to get involved,

01:07:57.880 --> 01:08:02.032
men think it's because
they were messed with as a kid?

01:08:02.080 --> 01:08:04.116
They were messed with as a woman.

01:08:04.160 --> 01:08:06.310
I'm not gonna mess with you.

01:08:07.360 --> 01:08:09.999
Do you like my tuna?

01:08:10.040 --> 01:08:12.270
Yeah, it's good.

01:08:13.240 --> 01:08:16.835
You didn't graduate high school,
so what? You can go back.

01:08:16.880 --> 01:08:21.158
Go back? I don't think so. I had one
highlight in high school, one.

01:08:21.200 --> 01:08:23.236
What was that?

01:08:23.279 --> 01:08:27.273
I played Sister Sarah
in our production of Guys And Dolls.

01:08:27.319 --> 01:08:29.435
No kidding.

01:08:29.479 --> 01:08:32.756
- Frankie and Johnny.
- I've heard the song.

01:08:32.800 --> 01:08:36.236
- We were a couple before we met.
