01:10:33.000 --> 01:10:34.592
Let's bowl.

01:10:37.440 --> 01:10:39.431
Now, concentrate, Cora.

01:10:48.480 --> 01:10:52.029
Here we go, Frankie.
Need this spare, honey. Go!

01:10:52.080 --> 01:10:55.675
Watch this. Watch! Beautiful!

01:11:06.640 --> 01:11:08.631
- Hell.
- Great, Nedda.

01:11:08.680 --> 01:11:11.240
- It was two.
- It was better than last time.

01:11:18.320 --> 01:11:21.312
- You see that?
- Where'd you learn to bowl so good?

01:11:21.360 --> 01:11:23.828
Altoona, PA.
