01:11:29.520 --> 01:11:31.556
You're from Altoona?

01:11:33.160 --> 01:11:36.596
I think I'm going to have
some kind of fit.

01:11:38.320 --> 01:11:41.312
I was born in Altoona.

01:11:41.360 --> 01:11:44.432
- Very funny.
