01:12:45.960 --> 01:12:48.633
Anyway, the old guy says to me...

01:12:48.680 --> 01:12:50.989
Are we bowling or what?

01:12:52.360 --> 01:12:55.716
Sorry. Shall we bowl?

01:12:55.760 --> 01:12:58.228
That's why he has such a good memory.

01:12:58.280 --> 01:13:01.477
He can't bowl in those shoes.
What is wrong with him?

01:13:01.520 --> 01:13:04.034
I'm gonna use my own little ball.

01:13:25.680 --> 01:13:28.478
Come on, Frankie, pull another one!

01:13:48.520 --> 01:13:50.636
- How you doin'?
- OK.

01:13:50.680 --> 01:13:53.114
You all right?

