doctor mine.

01:14:25.960 --> 01:14:28.554
I'm going all over the place
with you.

01:14:28.600 --> 01:14:30.955
I don't know
what you're talking about.

01:14:31.000 --> 01:14:33.309
I'm in love with you. I love you.

01:14:33.360 --> 01:14:37.717
I am totally, completely mad for you.
My heart stops every time I see you.

01:14:37.760 --> 01:14:40.035
I think we should be married.

01:14:40.080 --> 01:14:43.038
I definitely want kids.
